{"title":"Kali Keeps Your Head Protected wherever the Road Takes You with New Uno Helmet","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/03/09/kali-keeps-your-head-protected-wherever-the-road-takes-you-with-new-uno-helmet/","date":1615304601000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p>Kali Protectives is known for delivering innovative technology to keep people safe, drawing from extensive experience in motorsports to create engineering-driven options for cyclists no matter where the ride takes them. The new Uno helmet from the Morgan Hill, CA based company brings a lightweight, well ventilated option to the table, and it’s packed with the innovative safety features Kali is known for to make sure you’re protected whether you’re sticking to tarmac or hitting some gravel.</p><p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06144433/Kali-Uno-Action.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x323/rscb8/ng:webp/ngcb8\" alt=\"Kali Uno Riders\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06144433/Kali-Uno-Action.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x323/rscb8/ng:webp/ngcb8\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06144433/Kali-Uno-Action.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06144433/Kali-Uno-Action-297x198.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06144433/Kali-Uno-Action-800x533.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06144433/Kali-Uno-Action-120x80.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.c