-content/uploads/2021/03/06144648/Kali-Uno-Rear.jpg\" alt=\"Kali Uno Rear View\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06144648/Kali-Uno-Rear.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06144648/Kali-Uno-Rear.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06144648/Kali-Uno-Rear-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06144648/Kali-Uno-Rear-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06144648/Kali-Uno-Rear-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06144648/Kali-Uno-Rear-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06144648/Kali-Uno-Rear-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06144648/Kali-Uno-Rear-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06144648/Kali-Uno-Rear-630x420.jpg 630w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06144648/Kali-Uno-Rear.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06144648/Kali-Uno-Rear-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06144648/Kali-Uno-Rear-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06144648/Kali-Uno-Rear-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06144648/Kali-Uno-Rear-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06144648/Kali-Uno-Rear-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06144648/Kali-Uno-Rear-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06144648/Kali-Uno-Rear-630x420.jpg 630w\"></p><p>The Uno features 16 vents, including three “Supervents” to keep airflow up and your head cool. Each of the three forward facing “Supervents” is designed to increase the structural integrity around the vent allowing for a larger vent size and more airflow without compromising protection.</p><p>Inside, Kali employs their proprietary Quad Core Low Density Layer to combat linear and rotational impact forces, with the pads dispersed around the interior to channel airflow over the head and through the helmet. The Uno’s main structure is comprised of Contego 3 EPS foam that is optimized specifically for protective helmets and designed to take the brunt of the larger impacts, working in conjunction with the Quad Core Low Density Layer to provide a holistic approach to protecting riders.</p><figure id=\"attachment_252614\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-252614\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06145135/Kali-Uno-Gravel-Rider.jpg\" alt=\"Kali Uno on Gravel\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06145135/Kali-Uno-Gravel-Rider.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06145135/Kali-Uno-Gravel-Rider.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06145135/Kali-Uno-Gravel-Rider-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06145135/Kali-Uno-Gravel-Rider-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06145135/Kali-Uno-Gravel-Rider-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06145135/Kali-Uno-Gravel-Rider-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06145135/Kali-Uno-Gravel-Rider-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06145135/Kali-Uno-Gravel-Rider-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06145135/Kali-Uno-Gravel-Rider-630x420.jpg 630w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06145135/Kali-Uno-Gravel-Rider.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06145135/Kali-Uno-Gravel-Rider-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06145135/Kali-Uno-Gravel-Rider-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06145135/Kali-Uno-Gravel-Rider-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06145135/Kali-Uno-Gravel-Rider-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06145135/Kali-Uno-Gravel-Rider-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06145135/Kali-Uno-Gravel-Rider-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06145135/Kali-Uno-Gravel-Rider-630x420.jpg 630w\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-252614\">The Uno is designed to keep riders cool and protected no matter where the “road” turns</figcaption></figure><p>Anti-microbial fit pads and a micro-fit closure system keep the Uno comfortably in place through all the bumps the road or trail can throw at you.</p><figure id=\"attachment_252611\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-252611\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06143757/Kali-Uno-Colors.jpg\" alt=\"Kali Uno Color Lineup\" width=\"1200\" height=\"446\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06143757/Kali-Uno-Colors.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06143757/Kali-Uno-Colors.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06143757/Kali-Uno-Colors-297x110.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06143757/Kali-Uno-Colors-800x297.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06143757/Kali-Uno-Colors-120x45.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06143757/Kali-Uno-Colors-768x285.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06143757/Kali-Uno-Colors-696x259.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06143757/Kali-Uno-Colors-1068x397.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06143757/Kali-Uno-Colors-1130x420.jpg 1130w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06143757/Kali-Uno-Colors.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06143757/Kali-Uno-Colors-297x110.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06143757/Kali-Uno-Colors-800x297.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06143757/Kali-Uno-Colors-120x45.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06143757/Kali-Uno-Colors-768x285.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06143757/Kali-Uno-Colors-696x259.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06143757/Kali-Uno-Colors-1068x397.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/06143757/Kali-Uno-Colors-1130x420.jpg 1130w\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-252611\">The Uno is available in Solid Matte Black, Solid Matte Black/Red, Solid Matte Black/White, Solid Gloss Blue/White, and Camo Matte Thunder</figcaption></figure><p>The Uno is offered in two sizes – S/M to suit 54-58cm heads and L/XL for heads sized 58-61cm. Kali threw the Uno on the scales for us with the S/M weighing in at 298g and the L/XL at 324g. Five colorway options let you match your favorite gear, and the despite all the features the Uno won’t break the bank with an MSRP of $100 USD.</p><p>Due to the supply-chain disruptions resulting from the pandemic affecting many cycling industry companies, the Uno is out of stock on <a href=\"https://kaliprotectives.com/products/uno?variant=32134574997598\">Kali’s direct to consumer web store</a> – however they promise wider availability come fall ’21, and if you can’t wait you can always head to your local Kali stocking dealer where they’ve prioritized fulfilling orders.</p></div></div>","author":"Chris Chou","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"318f212bb341870b23194169e8b66537331d1ff1fd4335b2c2e7401c7b71e457","category":"Cycling"}